aint, pencils and pastels. A hallmark of the Art Academy franchise is its easy-to-follow lessons with step-by-step guides that teach painting and drawing techniques. A friendly tutor takes students of all ages through these lessons, each of which breaks down complex-looking images into simple steps. Gradually, players pick up more new techniques that allow anyone to create artwork they can be proud of.", "themes": [{"id": 34, "name": "Educational"}], "url": "https://www.igdb.com/games/pokemon-art-academy", "videos": [{"id": 2675, "name": "Trailer", "video_id": "gQhCMZSZXHU", "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gQhCMZSZXHU", "title": "Pok\u00e9mon Art Academy - Trailer (Nintendo 3DS)", "thumb": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi/gQhCMZSZXHU/maxresdefault.jpg"}], "collections": [{"id": 2511, "name": "Art Academy"}]}